The **Vocabulary Notebook** page (`src/pages/Vocabulary.tsx`) is implemented with:

- **Full CRUD** — add, edit, delete vocabulary entries with all 13 fields from the `VocabularyEntry` model
- **Search** — fuzzy search across word, meaning, Vietnamese meaning, and example sentences
- **Filters** — by IELTS topic, status (`new`/`learning`/`reviewing`/`mastered`), difficulty (`easy`/`medium`/`hard`), and tags (auto-collected from existing entries)
- **Quick actions** — mark as mastered (checkmark button), mark as difficult (warning button), edit, delete
- **Statistics** — 6 stats cards: total, new, learning, reviewing, mastered, hard words
- **Detail view** — click a word to see all its info in a modal with collocations/synonyms/antonyms chips
- **Data persistence** — all operations go through IndexedDB via the existing `db.ts` layer
- **Routing** — wired up in `Layout.tsx` at `/vocabulary` replacing the placeholder
